author: cbs8
title: People form human chain to protest gun violence
text:
SAN DIEGO (CBS 8) - Dozens of people gathered in Pioneer Park in Mission Hills Wednesday to protest gun violence.
People linked their arms to form a human chain along the perimeter of the park. The event organized by the San Diego Chapter of the Brady Campaign to prevent gun violence.
Participants say they hope the demonstration lets lawmakers know people want action on gun control.
